{"tid":161037,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新Matrix電影非Reboot 將繼承前作世界觀","createTime":"2017-03-18T08:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T10:57:17.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f67448f6d029541fb8f707e4f0082bfff46ceefc","tid":161037,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"如果各位擔心駭客任務是世界觀重啟的人，目前可以放心一下，因為被華納選為負責的編劇 Zak Penn 在自己推特說到他們也認為重啟或者重製原有三部曲不妥，言下之意重啟這個字眼是指政策上的重啟，會用不同角度和角色去探索其世界觀，簡單來說就是類似侏羅紀公園和侏羅紀世界的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;All I can say at this point is no one could or should REBOOT the Matrix. People who know Animatrix and the comics understand.&nbsp;Can&rsquo;t comment yet except to say that the words &ldquo;reboot&rdquo; and &ldquo;remake&rdquo; were from an article. Let&rsquo;s stop responding to inaccurate news.&nbsp;If I were going to recast Keanu Reeves, I would cast Keanu Reeves.&nbsp;How about just re-release the matrix? Don&rsquo;t reboot it, you can&rsquo;t do better.&nbsp;Do I want to see more stories set in the universe of the matrix? Yes. Because it&rsquo;s a brilliant idea that generates great stories.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://heroichollywood.com/new-matrix-film-will-not-be-a-reboot/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fheroichollywood.com%2Fnew-matrix-film-will-not-be-a-reboot%2F&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=304c40dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://heroichollywood.com/new-matrix-film-will-not-be-a-reboot/</a>"},{"pid":"7d50f380388057fd7934c4149e423f5dc49e2d1d","tid":161037,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"唔通又嚟多次人類總要重複相同錯誤，定3集入面插啲故事嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341454362cbd9d8c1079bf0b04f5e53b69df985f","tid":161037,"uid":37101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通又嚟多次人類總要重複相同錯誤，定3集入面插啲故事嚟講<img src=\"/assets/fa